calm nights in >>

my skin’s been loving this combo lately🤍 ad

I recently started using the @cosrx 6 Peptide Skin Booster Serum, and my skin feels smoother and more balanced. It’s lightweight, non greasy, hydrating, and absorbs quickly. It’s has calming ingredients like panthenol and allantoin, which helps soothe and calm irritation and redness.

Then the cult-favorite, @klairs.global Midnight Blue Calming Cream. I’ve been using it for quite a while, and this is my second tube. It’s a gentle soothing cream that helps calm redness and inflammation. It has this beautiful blue color that comes from Guaiazulene, know for its calming and soothing properties. If my skin’s feeling a bit red or sensitive, this cream does an amazing job of just soothing everything.

available on @maccaron_beauty
